Email Sending (Queued for Performance)
Step-by-Step Logic
Create a Mailable (Email Template)

bash
php artisan make:mail OrderConfirmation
Design Email (Blade Template)

php
// resources/views/emails/order.blade.php
<h1>Order #{{ $order->id }} Confirmed!</h1>
Send Email (From Controller/Listener)

php
Mail::to($user)->send(new OrderConfirmation($order));
Queue for Faster Responses

php
Mail::to($user)->queue(new OrderConfirmation($order));
Requires Redis/database queue setup.
